title: DAZ3D - Kahu for Kimo 7

KAHU FOR KIMO 7
---------------

Kahu is a sun-kissed Polynesian inspired young hunk for Kimo 7. Kahu includes Custom Sculpted HD Head and Body Morphs to give Kimo 7 a unique new look. Kahu includes 6 eye and two anatomical element mats. The skin was crafted from high-res photos and the textures are based on Genesis 3 Male Base UV maps
